    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    HomeController
    Handles login page display and form submission.
    LoginForm
    Represents the data submitted by the user in the login form.
    MilestoneprojectApplication
    Entry point for the Spring Boot application.
    Profile
    Profile is a model class representing a user's fitness and personal details.
    ProfileController
    ProfileController is responsible for handling all web requests related to user profile creation and editing.
    ProfileService
    ProfileService is a service layer class responsible for managing profile-related operations such as creating and storing new profiles.
    ProfileServiceInterface
    ProfileServiceInterface defines the contract for profile-related operations within the application.
    RegistrationController
    Handles user registration requests, including displaying the registration form and processing form submissions.
    RegistrationForm
    RegistrationForm is a model class that represents the data submitted by a user during registration.
    RegistrationService
    Handles user registration logic and communication with the repository.
    RegistrationServiceInterface
    Defines the methods for user registration services.
    SecurityService
    Handles user authentication by checking login credentials.
    SecurityServiceInterface
    Defines the contract for user authentication services.
    UserEntity
    Represents a user in the system and maps to the "users" table in the database.
    UserRepository
    Repository for accessing and managing user data in the database.
    Workout
    Model class representing a Workout.
    WorkoutController
    Handles workout-related requests, including logging and viewing workouts.
    WorkoutEntity
    Represents a workout record in the system and maps to the "workout" table.
    WorkoutRepository
    Repository for accessing and managing workout records in the database.
    WorkoutService
    Handles workout logging and retrieval operations.
    WorkoutServiceInterface
    Defines the methods for managing user workouts.
